<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Cobra Kai</title>
</head>

<body class="container text-light">
    <div class="inner-container">
        <header>
            <h1><img style="width: 2em" src="/images/logo.png"> Cobra Kai Dojo</h1>
        </header>

        <div class="row">
            <!-- about & join -->
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
                <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow text-white bg-dark">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="mb-4">About</h2>
                        <p>Welcome to the Cobra Kai Karate dojo â€“ where legacy meets modernity and strength meets
                            discipline. As successors of the legendary karate tradition, we honor the past while
                            fearlessly forging the future. </p>
                        <p>In our dojo, we believe that karate is more than just a martial art; it's a way of life,
                            instilling values of respect, perseverance, and indomitable spirit. Our world-class
                            instructors are committed to nurturing every student's potential, regardless of their age or
                            skill level. </p>
                        <p>Strike first, strike hard, no mercy - this is the Cobra Kai way. Welcome to the family.</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-danger mt-4" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#task-form" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="task-form">Join
                            Cobra Kai</button>
                        <div class="collapse" id="task-form">
                            <div id="message"></div>
                            <form class="mt-4" id="registerForm">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                        <label for="username" class="form-label">Name</label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" required>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                        <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Become badass</button>
                                <button id="loginButton" class="btn btn-danger">Already Badass? Login here...</button>
                            </form>
                            <form class="mt-4" id="loginForm" style="display: none;">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                        <label for="login-username" class="form-label">Name</label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="login-username" required>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                                        <label for="login-password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="login-password">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Log in</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- news -->
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
                <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow text-white bg-dark">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="mb-4">Latest news</h2>
                        <div class="card text-white bg-dark">
                            <img src="/images/cobrakai.png" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Get ready to witness the spirit of Karate in its purest form at the
                                    highly anticipated All Valley Tournament! </p>
                                <p class="card-text">This year, we're bringing stronger competitors, fiercer battles,
                                    and unforgettable moments.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-5">
            <!-- Section 3: Weekly Schedule -->
            <div class="col">
                <h2 class="mb-4t">Schedule</h2>
                <div class="table-responsive">
                    <table class="table table-bordered table-sm text-light" id="scheduleTable">
                        
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>


</body>

</html>